org.timepedia.chronoscope.client.plot
Class RangePanel

java.lang.Object
  org.timepedia.chronoscope.client.plot.RangePanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Panel
public final class RangePanel
extends java.lang.Object

Represents the vertical range axes to the left and right of the center plot panel. Both the left and right panel are drawn onto the same Layer.

Author:
chad takahashi
